🧵 TKT — Image Optimization & Resize System (HotLapHQ)

⸻

🎯 Objective

Reduce page weight from ~20MB → <3MB by:
	•	Serving correctly sized images
	•	Avoiding full-resolution downloads
	•	Using CloudFront caching
	•	Generating images on-demand (once)
	•	Persisting resized images in S3

⸻

🧠 Final Architecture

Flow

Browser
  ↓
CloudFront (cache)
  ↓
S3 (derived images)
  ↓ (if 404)
Lambda (Sharp)
  ↓
S3 (store generated images)
  ↓
CloudFront caches


